metadata.name: Goddess of Oceans
metadata.description:
Shapeshifter and Goddess of the Oceans, Thetis tames it and seeks to replenish the balance for its thalassic inhabitants. Thetis rises up against the tyranny of human disrespect for ocean environments and its precious ecosystem.

Made with procreate.

Dimensions:
3000 x 3000 px
300 DPI
PNG Format
